title: Tummy Tucks & Getting The Cops Called on Me
description:
This week Camo and Tasia talk plastic surgery, raising children unsheltered, and TikTok drama. Tune in to hear Tasia and Camo talk about jealous creators, the glamorization of drugs and alcohol on TikTok, and the difference between fame and following. Camo also updates everyone on the neighbor drama from last week and things get intense!!
